07:52:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.filmcritics.org.hk/film-review/node/2017/06/09/%E6%84%9B%E6%83%85%E8%A7%80%E8%87%AA%E5%9C%A8%EF%BC%9A%E8%87%AA%E5%9C%A8%E6%84%9B%E6%83%85%E8%A7%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.filmcritics.org.hk%2Ffilm-review%2Fnode%2F2017%2F06%2F09%2F%25E6%2584%259B%25E6%2583%2585%25E8%25A7%2580%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%259C%25A8%25EF%25BC%259A%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%2584%259B%25E6%2583%2585%25E8%25A7%2580&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm3Kg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=5445ea83\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.filmcritics.org.hk/film-review/node/2017/06/09/%E6%84%9B%E6%83%85%E8%A7%80%E8%87%AA%E5%9C%A8%EF%BC%9A%E8%87%AA%E5%9C%A8%E6%84%9B%E6%83%85%E8%A7%80</a><br />\n<br />\n愛情觀自在：自在愛情觀<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">看山是山，看水是水</span>"},{"pid":"3abb437abb80b02c332b1717a9e6912ff90c313d","tid":2420204,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a25e0ebb541e9b90bd12f26e00ad40e658f051e","tid":2420204,"uid":268578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1e3fc0c6a9cc4756138b98b7943e3d0b8864371","tid":2420204,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5570d3c05f7f7915e8e8049a592dbbb045d23f34","tid":2420204,"uid":61277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T19:18:15.000Z","msg":"萬般皆空<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n利申空宗撚"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:36:26.000Z","msg":"如果我搶人條女，同邊個結果？男嘅？女嘅？個果又有幾大？<br />\n點樣做到萬般皆空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我睇靚女一樣會勃起，點樣先做到咩看相無相嘅階段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:49:14.000Z","msg":"唔係話唔會勃起，而係隨佢勃起<br />\n<br />\n花開花落，勃起落下，緣起緣滅，感覺會黎就會走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T18:21:50.000Z","msg":"認真，學到嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b8076a411ddf350547de6a0ea80f12cb094b8f8","tid":2420204,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a25e0ebb541e9b90bd1